# gitignore for a study folder

# debugging / scratch — may contain answers, course material under licence
.study/current-questions.md

# personal exam attempts may contain identifying info
exams/*/my-attempt.md

# raw lecture transcripts may be under copyright; review per source
# (uncomment if your material is licensed and shouldn't be committed)
# material/transcripts/
# material/readings/
# material/lectures/
